
ikaaro 0.60.7 (2010/01/25)
==========================

This is a Content Management System built on Python & itools, among
other features ikaaro provides:

 - content and document management (index&search, metadata, etc.)
 - multilingual user interfaces and content
 - high level modules: wiki, forum, tracker, etc.

Now the icms-stop.py script takes the --force optional argument, it
will cancel the ongoing requests and immediately stop the server.

Now the mail spool keeps the messages that could not be sent in the
'spool/failed' folder.

Many bugs have been fixed, including #762.


